The paper deals with optimization of submodular and supermodular functions, which are fundamental concepts in computer science and optimization. The paper also mentions applications in maximum entropy sampling and column-subset selection, which are related to machine learning and data analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
